</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm308404416">
<problem id="fs-idm475430384">
<para id="fs-idm441528768">How were the immigrants regarded by American-born workers? How did many factory owners regard the influx of immigrants in the Gilded Age?</para>
</problem>
